        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Locality-based Social Security Benefits Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Social Security Administration to increase an individual's monthly Social Security benefit amount&nbsp;in&nbsp;accordance with the locality-based comparability payment rate applicable to the federal locality-pay area in which the individual resides.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
